      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>remaining cornflour</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong>, the <strong>five-spice mix</strong>,<strong> </strong>1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
